Feature: ACT-10 - Order History Date Range
  As a shopper, I require the ability to filter
  my order history by the date range specified so
  I can narrow down my purchase history.

  @pending
  Scenario: VIR-235.01 Verify that the shopper can view the order history within My Account

  @pending
  Scenario: VIR-235.02 Verify that the newest order is shown first in the list

  @pending
  Scenario: VIR-235.03 Verify that the orders can be filtered by
  Examples:
  |filter|
  |date|
  |by year|
  |placed half a year ago|
  |placed last 30 days|

  @pending
  Scenario: VIR-235.04 Verify that the current year view of orders is set by default

  @pending
  Scenario: VIR-235.05 Verify that the orders can be sorted by
  Examples:
  |sort|
  |PO #|
  |Ship to|

  @pending
  Scenario: VIR-235.06 Verify that the orders can be grouped by PO# (alpha-numeric)